script.name: !setup.x3fl
script.sourceplaintext:
$start.group = get game start group id do if $start.group == 100 return null
$previous.load = get global variable: name='x3fl.load'
$page.id = 1907 set global variable: name='st.ex.pageid' value=$page.id $kingdom.end = get sector from universe index: x=0, y=0 set global variable: name='main.universe' value=$kingdom.end
@ START [THIS] -> call script !station.shieldstock.terran : @ START [THIS] -> call script !lib.war.watch : @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.expguild.run : @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.sewn.run : @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.st.ex.setup : @ START [THIS] -> call script graph.data.collector :
add god exclusion: resource=Slaves add god exclusion: resource=Pirate Sidearms add god exclusion: product=Mercenary add god exclusion: product=Marine
add god factory removal exclusion: race=Terran add god factory removal exclusion: race=ATF add god factory removal exclusion: race=Yaki add god factory removal exclusion: race=Strong Arms
$gaian.star = get sector from universe index: x=18, y=12 if $gaian.star -> exists $st.ex = find station in galaxy: startsector=$gaian.star class or type=Pirate Stock Exchange race=Pirates flags=[Find.Multiple] refobj=null serial=null max.jumps=30 if is datatype[ $st.ex ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $i = size of array $st.ex while $i dec $i = $st = $st.ex[$i] $st.ex -> set stock exchange unlock state: [TRUE] end else if $st.ex -> exists $st.ex -> set stock exchange unlock state: [TRUE] end end
$terran.gate = get sector from universe index: x=4, y=6 if $terran.gate -> exists $flags = [Find.ExcludeGates] | [Find.ExcludeTerranGates] | [Find.Hyperspeed] $terran.gate = find gate: flags=$flags, refobj=$terran.gate, max dist=null, refpos=null if $terran.gate -> exists $terran.gate ->set owner race to Argon $terran.gate = $terran.gate -> get gate destination: return sector=[FALSE] $terran.gate ->set owner race to Argon end end
if $start.group == 200 $is.open = [FALSE] $sector = get sector from universe index: x=14, y=14 if $sector -> exists $flags = [Find.Multiple] $gates = find gate: flags=$flags, refobj=$sector, max dist=null, refpos=null if $gates if is datatype[ $gates ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $size = size of array $gates do if $size > 1 $is.open = [TRUE] end end
$sectors = array alloc: size=14 $sectors[0] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=14, y=15 $sectors[1] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=14, y=16 $sectors[2] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=14, y=17 $sectors[3] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=13, y=16 $sectors[4] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=15, y=16 $sectors[5] = $sector
$sector = get sector from universe index: x=18, y=16 $sectors[6] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=18, y=17 $sectors[7] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=18, y=18 $sectors[8] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=18, y=19 $sectors[9] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=17, y=17 $sectors[10] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=17, y=18 $sectors[11] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=19, y=18 $sectors[12] = $sector $sector = get sector from universe index: x=20, y=18 $sectors[13] = $sector
$i = size of array $sectors while $i dec $i = $sector = $sectors[$i] if $sector -> exists if $is.open remove god exclusion: sector=$sector else add god exclusion: sector=$sector end end end end end
* register hotkeys $cbh.page.id = 6024
$id = register hotkey event script: script=plugin.turbo.hotkey, type=[Input.Upgrades], page id=[Page.Input], text id=1000000, key=90000 set global variable: name='hotkey.turbo' value=$id $id = register hotkey: script=plugin.turbo.toggle, type=[Input.Upgrades], page id=[Page.Input], text id=1000003, menu=[FALSE], key=null set global variable: name='hotkey.turbo.toggle' value=$id
$id = register hotkey: script=plugin.gz.turret.onoff.hotkey, type=[Input.Weapons], page id=[Page.Input], text id=1000001, menu=[FALSE], key=null $id = register hotkey: script=plugin.hotkey.launchdrone, type=[Input.Weapons], page id=[Page.Input], text id=1000002, menu=[FALSE], key=null $id = register hotkey: script=plugin.hotkey.launchmarines, type=[Input.Weapons], page id=[Page.Menus], text id=4761, menu=[FALSE], key=null $id = register hotkey: script=plugin.hotkey.launchbarrage, type=[Input.Weapons], page id=[Page.Menus], text id=4762, menu=[FALSE], key=null
register custom object info: id='stationmgr', class=Station, script=plugin.stationmgr.info
if $previous.load $done.sectors = table alloc $x = get max sectors in x direction while $x dec $x = $y = get max sectors in y direction while $y dec $y = $sector = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y skip if $sector -> exists continue do if $done.sectors[$sector] continue $sector.owner = $sector -> get owner race skip if $sector.owner -> exists continue $flags = [Find.ExcludeTerranGates] | [Find.ExcludeGates] | [Find.Hyperspeed] | [Find.Multiple] $gates = find gate: flags=$flags, refobj=$sector, max dist=null, refpos=null if $gates if not is datatype[ $gates ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $gates = create new array, arguments=$gates, null, null, null, null end $i = size of array $gates while $i dec $i = $gate = $gates[$i] $dest.sector = $gate -> get gate destination: return sector=[TRUE] $done.sectors[$dest.sector] = [TRUE] $dest.gate = $gate -> get gate destination: return sector=[FALSE]
if $gate -> is known if not $gate ->is hyperspeed locked if not $gate ->is hyperspeed destination hidden $dest.gate ->set hsap destination hidden: [FALSE] $dest.gate ->set hsap locked: [FALSE] $dest.gate ->set known status to [TRUE] end end end if $dest.gate -> is known if not $dest.gate ->is hyperspeed locked if not $dest.gate ->is hyperspeed destination hidden $gate ->set hsap destination hidden: [FALSE] $gate ->set hsap locked: [FALSE] $gate ->set known status to [TRUE] end end end end end end end end
if not $previous.load add encyclopedia custom article: Manual, id='dynrace', title page=[Page.Encyclopedia], title id=1030011, text page=[Page.Encyclopedia], text id=1030012, group page=[Page.Encyclopedia], group id=1030001, group sort order=1, notify=[FALSE] add encyclopedia custom article: Manual, id='agents', title page=[Page.Encyclopedia], title id=1030021, text page=[Page.Encyclopedia], text id=1030022, group page=[Page.Encyclopedia], group id=1030001, group sort order=1, notify=[FALSE]

* Graphs add player graph: event script=graph.draw.networth pageid=[Page.QMenus] textid=1026 group pageid=null group textid=null subgroup=0 (0-7) add player graph: event script=graph.draw.multi.station.net pageid=[Page.Menus] textid=1104699 group pageid=[Page.Menus] group textid=1104707 subgroup=0 (0-7) add player graph: event script=graph.draw.multi.station.profit pageid=[Page.Menus] textid=1104705 group pageid=[Page.Menus] group textid=1104707 subgroup=0 (0-7) add player graph: event script=graph.draw.multi.station.total pageid=[Page.Menus] textid=1104702 group pageid=[Page.Menus] group textid=1104707 subgroup=0 (0-7)
* Additionoal setup $version = get global variable: name='x3fl.load' if not $version @ START [THIS] -> call script !lib.updaterelations : Delay Start=10000 Race=Duke's Force=[TRUE]
* tag asteroids for discovery $points = 1200000
$asteroids = table alloc $x = get max sectors in x direction while $x dec $x = $y = get max sectors in y direction while $y dec $y = $sector = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y skip if $sector -> exists continue
$sector.astro = $sector ->get asteroid table from sector $asteroids = merge tables, $asteroids, $sector.astro, null, null, null end end
while $points > 0 * just incase we dont hav enough asteroids skip if size of table $asteroids break
if $points < 3000 $p = $points else $p = random value from 1000 to 3000 - 1 end
do if $p > $points $p = $points
$a = get random key: table=$asteroids if $a -> exists $a ->set discovery points: points=$p $points = $points - $p end end end
set global variable: name='x3fl.load' value=1
return null
